oing to the keep and that is all, if I can find refuge there it will be over with and you can go to your home you can go back to Freeport where the curruption has not take so much. Please Yavi, if you fight, if you do this it will only mean you have been taken again.&quot; Tears were forming in her young eyes. &quot;Please, I don't want to have to pull you from that place again. Let us just go, if they want to cross us, I will handle it, but please Yavi, you have enough scars on your heart.&quot; Lowering his sword slowly. &quot;Young one, I will not be pulled into the darkness again, it is you that I am to protect and I will not let another scar on my soul be reason for my lack of my duty. We will go to this keep, and I will not go home until you are fully trained and then I will see to your return home to the forest of light. Where the stars sing and you can dance with the sky. But until then we must both suffer this evil wood and find the only shelter we can.&quot; Glaring at the small group, Yavi turned his gaze back to the woods. &quot;And all of you beware, we are not alone in the darkness. Something comes close.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bfantasystoriesforum.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bonaki>Bonaki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/15/02 3:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Forna</span><hr size=1> (ooc- hey umm.. Dahnyella.. right? opened a spot for ya. hope ya want to join in cause we could use all the peeps we can get. so jump right in here. Thanks for compliment Rillen, It is hard to have two at once, sometimes I forget who I'm typing for and have to start all over again haha too muc